data.description:
Located in the Bay Isle section of prestigious Plantation Bay gated golf community of Ormond Beach Florida.  Situated on a beautiful cul-de-sac lot. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath block home boasts an open floor plan with separate formal living and informal family areas.   Enjoy relaxing or entertaining in the spacious enclosed patio with no neighbors behind you for added privacy. Imagine waking up to nature views in your backyard with a designated fenced area that is perfect for your children or furry friends to play safely.Get ready to live the Florida Lifestyle when you choose this home. Walk or bike around all of the central ponds and fountains. Sit on a bench to take a rest while enjoying the many water views.Two clubhouses. A poolside Cabana bar for you to enjoy drinks and food as well as a great place to meet your neighbors.

State-of-the-art fitness, pool and spa complex.  Separate wellness center. 10 Har-Tru tennis courts in addition to 4 Pickleball courts, 2 Bocce and basketball courts. Three championship golf courses.

Nearby is the historic Ormond Beach Scenic Loop and Trail which can take you to the river or the ocean.

With a motivated seller offering this gem under market value, now is the perfect time to make this house your home sweet home! Priced for a quick sale.

All measurements are approximate.  All information should be verified by the buyer.
